        "content": "<p>I was working on <a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip/pull/21653\">#21653</a> which describes to grey out row for deactivated users in users table. The issue describes to use the colour used in notifications panel but currently we do not show muted streams in notification panel. So, I was thinking to use the colour used in left sidebar for muted streams. We have the following UI with that colour.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/a3/Wa449BT7_mIvellGu7A48BsQ/Screenshot-from-2023-07-12-21-38-04.png\">Light-mode.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/cd/VRWHTxplGqS96wa9j1pdM_-O/Screenshot-from-2023-07-12-21-34-52.png\">Dark-mode.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/a3/Wa449BT7_mIvellGu7A48BsQ/Screenshot-from-2023-07-12-21-38-04.png\" title=\"Light-mode.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/a3/Wa449BT7_mIvellGu7A48BsQ/Screenshot-from-2023-07-12-21-38-04.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/cd/VRWHTxplGqS96wa9j1pdM_-O/Screenshot-from-2023-07-12-21-34-52.png\" title=\"Dark-mode.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/cd/VRWHTxplGqS96wa9j1pdM_-O/Screenshot-from-2023-07-12-21-34-52.png\"></a></div><p>I think the screenshots looks good but would love to get some suggestions for colour.</p>",
